data.description: Covered front porch Welcomes You to this all brick 4Bdrm/2 ba home on 1.5 acres of beautifully landscaped lot. This home has all the extras you need, Heated Inground Pool, Lush Landscaping, Custom fencing and Concrete walk paths thru out the yard. There are 2 outdoor Buildings for all your storage needs as well as an extended concrete pad for RV/Boat parking. . Step inside to a Spacious  Family Rm with Fireplace. The open kitchen has Granite counters with lots of cabinet space. Don't let this one slip by! Its a Keeper!.
